# Business-cXML v0.6.5

[![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/vphantom/Business-cXML.svg?branch=v0.6.5)](https://travis-ci.org/vphantom/Business-cXML) [![Coverage Status](https://coveralls.io/repos/github/vphantom/Business-cXML/badge.svg?branch=v0.6.5)](https://coveralls.io/github/vphantom/Business-cXML?branch=v0.6.5)

Perl implementation of cXML messaging.

Dispatch incoming HTTP/HTTPS requests and respond to them.  Send outgoing
requests and parse responses.  Prepare and parse one-way messages.

## INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

## SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Business::cXML

If you find any bugs, please report them at:
	https://github.com/vphantom/Business-cXML/issues

## KNOWN BUGS

Microsoft Windows is not currently supported and I don't have access to such
an environment for testing.  See details in
https://github.com/vphantom/Business-cXML/issues/1

